The '''Common Mushroom''' is a mushroom found via [[foraging]] throughout Stardew Valley in the [[Fall]]. They can be found in the [[Secret Woods]] during [[Spring]] and [[Fall]], [[Farm Maps|Forest Farm]] during [[Summer]], and in the [[Ginger Island#Dig Site|Ginger Island mushroom cave]]. They can be grown from [[Fall Seeds|Wild Seeds (Fa)]] or in mushroom bins in the [[The Cave]] if the mushroom option is chosen. They can also be obtained by [[Tapper|tapping]] a [[Mushroom Tree]].  

Putting a Common Mushroom in a [[Seed Maker]] will generate 1-3 [[Fall Seeds]].

