==Tailoring==
Common Mushroom is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create a [[Tailoring|Shirt]]. [[File:Shirt074.png|24px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as an orange dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

This shirt is very likely a reference to the [[wikipedia:Super_Mario|Super Mario]] game series, where the titular character [[wikipedia:Mario|Mario]] commonly eats mushrooms.

==Quests==
*The Common Mushroom may be randomly requested in [[Fall]] at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|120}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.
*2-3 Common Mushrooms may be requested by [[Bullhead]], [[Largemouth Bass]], [[Midnight Carp]], or [[Woodskip]] in [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quests]].

==Trivia==
*Common Mushrooms are the only fall forageable that can be directly put into the [[Seed Maker]].

